text: V quiet and rare 999 leasehold condo with 2mins walk to nice beach/park. Right beside bus stop with only few stops to Pasir ris MRT, whitesands and downtown east shopping centers. Car park lots are conveniently located at ground level around lift landing and no need to navigate around basement.
A development directly beside the beach but it is a little deep from the main road and the development has an extremely small swimming pool.
Lovely and quite location. Opp to the Pasir Ris beach.  Greenery and fresh air around. Away from city hustle.
Simply love the quiet location and the beach which is stone throw away.
Great apartment blocks, loving the penthouse on top which has a view of the whole Pasir Ris coast.
